{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ergzk5yTRwkv3on2MGfFCi","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Development Full Workflow Reference\n     2→\n     3→## 상세 개발 워크플로우\n     4→\n     5→이 문서는 `develop/SKILL.md`의 상세 참조 문서이다.\n     6→\n     7→## 1. Entity 설계 상세\n     8→\n     9→### ID 전략\n    10→```kotlin\n    11→// UUID 기반 (기본)\n    12→@Id\n    13→@GeneratedValue(generator = \"uuid2\")\n    14→@GenericGenerator(name = \"uuid2\", strategy = \"uuid2\")\n    15→val id: String = \"\"\n    16→\n    17→// Auto Increment (특수한 경우)\n    18→@Id\n    19→@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)\n    20→val id: Long = 0\n    21→```\n    22→\n    23→### 관계 매핑\n    24→```kotlin\n    25→// ManyToOne (가장 흔함)\n    26→@ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n    27→@JoinColumn(name = \"user_id\")\n    28→val user: UserEntity? = null\n    29→\n    30→// referencedColumnName 지정 (PK가 아닌 컬럼 참조 시)\n    31→@ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n    32→@JoinColumn(name = \"category_id\", referencedColumnName = \"code\")\n    33→val category: CategoryEntity? = null\n    34→\n    35→// OneToMany (필요한 경우만)\n    36→@OneToMany(mappedBy = \"post\", fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n    37→val comments: List<CommentEntity> = emptyList()\n    38→```\n    39→\n    40→### Enum 매핑\n    41→```kotlin\n    42→// DB에 정수로 저장\n    43→@Column(nullable = false)\n    44→var status: Int = 0\n    45→\n    46→// Kotlin enum과 매핑\n    47→enum class UserStatus(val value: Int) {\n    48→    ACTIVE(0),\n    49→    INACTIVE(1),\n    50→    BANNED(2);\n    51→\n    52→    companion object {\n    53→        fun fromValue(value: Int) = entries.first { it.value == value }\n    54→    }\n    55→}\n    56→```\n    57→\n    58→## 2. Repository 상세\n    59→\n    60→### QueryDSL\n    61→```kotlin\n    62→interface CustomRepository {\n    63→    fun findByComplexCondition(userId: String, status: Int): List<Entity>\n    64→}\n    65→\n    66→class CustomRepositoryImpl(\n    67→    private val queryFactory: JPAQueryFactory,\n    68→) : CustomRepository {\n    69→    override fun findByComplexCondition(userId: String, status: Int): List<Entity> {\n    70→        val entity = QEntity.entity\n    71→        return queryFactory\n    72→            .selectFrom(entity)\n    73→            .where(\n    74→                entity.userId.eq(userId),\n    75→                entity.status.eq(status),\n    76→                entity.deletedAt.isNull,\n    77→            )\n    78→            .orderBy(entity.createdAt.desc())\n    79→            .fetch()\n    80→    }\n    81→}\n    82→```\n    83→\n    84→### Native Query\n    85→```kotlin\n    86→@Query(\"\"\"\n    87→    SELECT e.* FROM maum.entity e\n    88→    LEFT JOIN maum.other o ON e.id = o.entity_id\n    89→    WHERE e.user_id = :userId\n    90→    AND o.id IS NULL\n    91→\"\"\", nativeQuery = true)\n    92→fun findWithoutRelation(@Param(\"userId\") userId: String): List<Entity>\n    93→```\n    94→\n    95→## 3. gRPC 에러 처리 상세\n    96→\n    97→### 서버 측 (마이크로서비스)\n    98→```kotlin\n    99→override fun getFeature(\n   100→    request: GetFeatureRequest,\n   101→    responseObserver: StreamObserver<GetFeatureResponse>,\n   102→) {\n   103→    try {\n   104→        val result = service.getFeature(request.id)\n   105→        responseObserver.onNext(result.toProtoResponse())\n   106→        responseObserver.onCompleted()\n   107→    } catch (e: NotFoundException) {\n   108→        responseObserver.onError(\n   109→            Status.NOT_FOUND\n   110→                .withDescription(e.message)\n   111→                .asRuntimeException()\n   112→        )\n   113→    } catch (e: Exception) {\n   114→        responseObserver.onError(\n   115→            Status.INTERNAL\n   116→                .withDescription(\"Internal error\")\n   117→                .asRuntimeException()\n   118→        )\n   119→    }\n   120→}\n   121→```\n   122→\n   123→### 클라이언트 측 (GraphQL 모듈)\n   124→```kotlin\n   125→fun getFeature(id: String): GetFeatureResponse {\n   126→    return try {\n   127→        stub.getFeature(request)\n   128→    } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {\n   129→        when (e.status.code) {\n   130→            Status.Code.NOT_FOUND -> throw CustomGraphQLException(\"NOT_FOUND\", e.status.description)\n   131→            Status.Code.INVALID_ARGUMENT -> throw CustomGraphQLException(\"BAD_REQUEST\", e.status.description)\n   132→            else -> throw CustomGraphQLException(\"INTERNAL\", \"서비스 오류\")\n   133→        }\n   134→    }\n   135→}\n   136→```\n   137→\n   138→## 4. 트랜잭션 패턴\n   139→\n   140→```kotlin\n   141→@Service\n   142→class FeatureService(\n   143→    private val repository: FeatureRepository,\n   144→    private val eventPublisher: ApplicationEventPublisher,\n   145→) {\n   146→    // 읽기 전용\n   147→    @Transactional(readOnly = true)\n   148→    fun getById(id: String): Entity {\n   149→        return repository.findById(id).orElseThrow { NotFoundException(\"Not found: $id\") }\n   150→    }\n   151→\n   152→    // 쓰기 (기본)\n   153→    @Transactional\n   154→    fun create(input: CreateInput): Entity {\n   155→        val entity = Entity(name = input.name)\n   156→        return repository.save(entity)\n   157→    }\n   158→\n   159→    // 여러 Repository 사용\n   160→    @Transactional\n   161→    fun complexOperation(userId: String, input: Input): Result {\n   162→        val user = userRepository.findById(userId).orElseThrow()\n   163→        val entity = repository.save(Entity(userId = userId))\n   164→        historyRepository.save(History(entityId = entity.id, action = \"CREATE\"))\n   165→        return Result(entity)\n   166→    }\n   167→}\n   168→```\n   169→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_016jduMWZFu5DYZS28BwMaLx","session_id":"0a35d23b-1cee-492b-96cb-26ed17253e15","uuid":"7663f8f6-df5a-4722-9a82-0b1596da0e98"}
